{"tid":1689802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信救消防 消防做自己職責仲要俾高層照肺","createTime":"2019-11-03T04:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T18:10:52.000Z","uid":304992,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ac8dbbb235a7b9712bbca06fd97721a2cdb5ab","tid":1689802,"uid":304992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:10:59.000Z","msg":"落車同防暴理論嗰位消防師兄宜家俾好多藍絲追擊同起底。甚至動員寫信投訴，亦有傳佢比高層照肺。<br />\n<br />\n  金鐘消防員開閘單野，消防收左70000封信。好彩支持的比投訴的多好多。<br />\n消防為我地撐左好耐，宜家係時候報恩。<br />\n消防處好重視民意，如果多人寫信/電郵去讚佢，消防處真係可能為免激起民憤而放生佢！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請幫手電郵去表揚英勇消防員</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPYFPqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPYFPqw.jpg&h=cbfe533d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電郵地址<br />\ndfs@hkfsd.gov.hk , ddfs@hkfsd.gov.hk , hkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk , hkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk , kw_fstn@hkfsd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n*建議大家再個別改改不同的標題和內容<br />\n<br />\n參考一<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n表揚駕駛消防車（F328）的消防員盡忠職守<br />\n<br />\n消防處處長李建日先生、副處長梁偉雄先生、分區指揮官(港島中)湯忠偉先生、消防區長(港島中) 楊啟宏先生、港灣消防局局長劉宇傑先生：2019年11月2日約晚上7時半，有警員一度向停泊路邊消防車（F328）發射催淚彈，並命中該部消防車。車上消防員慘中催淚煙，但仍然盡忠職守，全力保護消防車。他下車與在場數十名防暴警理論，雙方發生口角。網上有影片拍攝全個過程（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leoball727/videos/498401254078967/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleoball727%2Fvideos%2F498401254078967%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=fd8626a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leoball727/videos/498401254078967/</a> ），影片所見防暴警大力將該名消防員推向牆邊，並以粗言穢語責罵該名消防員。<br />\n一直以來，無論在山上拯救被困人士(有消防員更曾為警察殉職)及火場中，消防處人員在承受極人風險的情況下工作，但現時消防處人員執勤竟被針對，以催淚彈攻擊及惡意推撞，如此惡劣工作環境實在非常不合理。請消防處今次能還受影響的前線消防員一個公道，並高度肯定每位消防人員的付出！<br />\n<br />\n一位關心香港的市民 XXX 上<br />\n<br />\n參考二<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n敬啟者<br />\n<br />\n在11月2日的公眾活動中，看見前線消防處人員盡力為保護市民提供緊急救援服務，本人特此讚揚消防處人員的付出。<br />\n但是，本人同時留意到消防處人員在十分危險的環境下工作。在［片段一］中，消防處人員在沒有任何裝備的情況下被警察胡亂地以催淚彈攻擊，當消防人員下車理論時更被多名蒙面警察推撞及粗暴對待！<br />\n一直以來，無論在山上拯救被困人士(有消防員更曾為警察殉職)及火場中，消防處人員在承受極人風險的情況下工作，但現時消防處人員執勤時竟然被警方無理針對及挑釁，並以催淚彈攻擊及意圖毆打，實在過份! 請消防處今次就事件還前線消防員一個公道，並立即譴責警方的暴力行為。 最後請高度肯定每位消防人員的付出！謝謝。<br />\n片段一：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaJ3QSyi_aU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTaJ3QSyi_aU&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c94db153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TaJ3QSyi_aU</a> <br />\n<br />\n一位關心香港的市民上<br />\n<br />\n來源: <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AB%8B%E5%B9%AB%E6%89%8B%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%E5%8E%BB%E8%A1%A8%E6%8F%9A%E8%8B%B1%E5%8B%87%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%2583%25B5%25E5%258E%25BB%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=2824ff99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%2583%25B5%25E5%258E%25BB%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1%2F&h=71c48d21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AB%8B%E5%B9%AB%E6%89%8B%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%E5%8E%BB%E8%A1%A8%E6%8F%9A%E8%8B%B1%E5%8B%87%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1/</a><br />\n<br />\n 參考三<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n標題：表揚及慰問在11月2日於中環執勤時被警方粗暴對待的消防員<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n消防設備是救災救人的重要工具，時刻檢查及確保消防設備的完好是一個消防員的專業職責。然而11月2日一名消防人員在中環出勤執行職務期間，所駕駛的消防車被警隊的催淚彈擊中，消防員馬上下車了解情況時並向在場警員表達意見。<br />\n讓人始料不及的是，在場的數十名警務人員非但未有為事件致歉，更呼喝、挑釁、推撞、圍堵在場的唯一一名消防員，事件讓人震驚及憤怒。<br />\n在場警員甚至馬上驅逐在場的記者朋友，令消防人員陷入孤立無援的境地，情況相當危急。<br />\n<br />\n在此，本人希望向這位消防人表達謝意及深切慰問！同時希望消防局不要因為政治壓力，扭曲消防員的守責行為。如此方不負社會對消防之期望！<br />\n<br />\n       此致<br />\n消防處長<br />\n<br />\n市民XXX<br />\n2019年11月3日<br />\n<br />\n［有圖］好多藍屍投訴消防講粗口，但一個人打電話去支持消防都無！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689029</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手打電話支持下F328消防員 順便投訴消防處副處長曱甴論 <br />\n亦可以建議一下為前線消防員做好保護措施<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnsLf6A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnsLf6A.png&h=c4968146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6afd9e9df96e4aa75e3320ae6260d7c297fd983","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"35f1c0fac39dc6c8cc8ba7b43bbbef78ffe38c1b","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c06f82f302f1e2a9b86caed5886c7f3fc15c1216","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59fb8b0b7201c6689930ac82212ce74e59cf71f2","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e175ab6a474746f2da5725a85629c5c6423de5f","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"點解冇人推嘅？"},{"pid":"47aca9b48752cac373cfa529f10e4e467d3ff058","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d6b79d36ebf63da38f7ba43fe11c346d32a66a7d","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b3dc3fc472b92cddfcafcb9af822a2967bb77ac7","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"91b9c9fbbe86368cd3ad8f50867c1ac5e630607d","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f7e8a8a1c009456088f08ea96b824a738f938bd0","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"28a0cae8b17fdddef22649b69c9a6ea79e68f8cc","tid":1689802,"uid":298893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"至緊要係個電郵地址啱，支持！"},{"pid":"dd2f25562dbefa931151851cca3141e45ef7044c","tid":1689802,"uid":284144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"支持消防 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d2be1d7174d1ee67b27e6474d6d45ca4c4b54e","tid":1689802,"uid":305200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"P仔推唔郁都幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4bad9709b0a0c4db31d9d30cd3d88b9ac37a5e","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"383663fe25ae1e5629f6faa5c75a3df6fb5ba24d","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3eb2ba5a5dffc859400727d1d41548ca2eace4c5","tid":1689802,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:00:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"814da30af4ec597b85b798fc2a59835e9db75f41","tid":1689802,"uid":42700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:01:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e48ebf726edb5416620c1c6872b2e5124c33797","tid":1689802,"uid":22088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56777f283155116634fddd0357f3a7329a1bbaab","tid":1689802,"uid":22088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:09:41.000Z","msg":"記住唔好自己個私人email"},{"pid":"646fd666261382f419496e614220468472c25f9b","tid":1689802,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:21:09.000Z","msg":"幫幫正義消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c062e46b3c841452396c8074d97af8aabceb3f5e","tid":1689802,"uid":142954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"已send"},{"pid":"ef37b0746437595529f86a7a9e3ee49f36cdfbea","tid":1689802,"uid":108692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af30e60882df625b8173fd184aabc8d33f6043b2","tid":1689802,"uid":229075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T22:12:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3c030a794cf8e2fb132c08b76bc294b378e0eeb6","tid":1689802,"uid":37234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:15:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}